sources.title: 2012 Ice Age + 2012 Doomsday | 2 Full Movies | Action Disaster Survival Double Feature
sources.description:
2012 Ice Age: A volcanic eruption in Iceland triggers a massive glacier, surging toward North America and freezing everything in its path. As a new ice age looms, one man fights to outrun the deadly cold, desperate to protect his family from the unstoppable wave of ice and destruction. Can they survive the coming freeze?
2011.  Stars: Patrick Labyorteaux, Julie McCullough ,Katie Wilson

2012 Doomsday: On December 21, 2012, four strangers, each on a personal journey of faith, find themselves drawn to an ancient temple deep in Mexico. For the Mayans, it marks the end of an era. NASA scientists warn of a cataclysmic polar shift. For the rest of the world, it signifies Doomsday. As the clock ticks down, their paths converge in a quest for meaning amid the impending chaos
2008.  Stars: Cliff De Young, Dale Midkiff, Ami Dolenz
